data.eml:eml: Acromyrmex charruanus: a new inquiline social parasite species of leaf-cutting ants

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article C. Rabeling, T. R. Schultz, M. Bacci Jr, M. Bollazzi (2015): Acromyrmex charruanus: a new inquiline social parasite species of leaf-cutting ants. Insectes Sociaux. 62: 335-349, DOI: 10.1007/s00040-015-0406-6
